$interpreted: Yan-Bo: ...Rare it is for you to come, yes. But find a human who wants to harm frogodiles, you say?
Yan-Bo: Such a person, resides here they do not.
Hestia: That's right! If you want to play games, this is not the place to do so! You hear that?
Karnulla: Nice try. Whenever strange humans make their way into Maple Lake, they always have something to do with you knuckleheads!
Karnulla: Always has been, always will!
Hestia: Then show us your proof!
Pang: Master Yan-Bo, I collected a human...
Pang: Eh? Karnulla?
Karnulla: Wait, is that her?
Karnulla: And there's your body of evidence! Now, what have you got to say!?
Yan-Bo: ...Oh my...tongue twisted am I...
Pang: What do you want?

Karnulla: Eye for an eye, tooth for a tooth. She injured one of
my bambinos, so I'm returning the favor. Scoot!
Pang: It was an accident, let it be.
Karnulla: Why do we always get the short end of the stick? NO FAIR!
Puggi: Lay a finger on the beauty and I'll show you who's the true beast! Come at me, ugly mouth!
Puggi: Pffft~ All bark and no bite, my swings and blows be like dynamite~
Karnulla: Argh! I'm definitely coming back to settle the score someday!
Puggi: Oh deary me!!
Karnulla: Hmph. Let's go!
Sharice: ...Ugh...where am I...?
Sharice: ......EH?
Sharice: AHH, AHHHH, it's the rat monster and the fish freak!
Sharice: You...you damn m-m-monsters...watch me...I-I-I'll show you...
Pang: You awake?
Hestia: Who you calling fish freak!
Yan-Bo: Enough with the anger...Tell us your name, young one.
Sharice: Hmph. Why should I tell you!?
Puggi: Well then, miss bliss, you feeling any discomfort~?
Puggi: Hoho~?
Sharice: You disgusting meatball, stay away from me!!!
Sharice: I, Sharice Carterwell will see to it that-
Pang: - Ah, so your name is Sharice Carterwell.
Sharice: ……….
Puggi: Haha~you told us anyway~
Sharice: Zip it, bird brain! Good thing I still have my spear! I'll send all of you to kingdom come!
Sharice: Ow ow ow, my neck...
Yan-Bo: Twisted neck there, I see?
Puggi: Puahaha~ She is always a second late. This is too much fun~
Sharice: Keep that mouth shut, none of your business!
Yan-Bo: A sprained neck, serious matter it may be. Lifelong paralyzation, affect lower body it could. Proper treatment, of most importance it is.
Sharice: You're kidding!?
Pang: Sharice got hurt because of Puggi. It's our duty to tend to her until she fully recovered.
Sharice: Don't call me by name, and I don't need your help!
Puggi: Guhehehehe...resistance is futile...just relax and we'll handle the rest for you~
Puggi: Guhehehehe~~~
Sharice: Noooooo!!!
